name: Jimmy's Durian Orchard
description: A medium-sized family run orchard located near Bentong, Pahang. We have approximately 300 trees that produce various varieties of durians such as Musang King, D24, tekka, D2, D101 and of course the classic "Durian Kampong". Visitors to our orchard may enjoy an educational talk by the owner, Jimmy where one can learn about the biology of the trees, how to identify varieties of durians and also most relevantly (and importantly!) how to choose a good durian. Rest assured that you will only be given fresh good quality durians! After stuffing yourself in the orchard, visitors are encouraged to buy and bring back durians, We offer quality that you just can't find in the city. Other than durians, the orchard also has mangosteens, rambutans, duku and a variety of local fruit.
